data.title: AMD ROCm 7.1.1 Released With RHEL 10.1 Support, More Models Working On RDNA4
data.description: Following the release of ROCm 7.1 from just under one month ago, ROCm 7.1.1 is now available with expanded Linux operating system support, continued Instinct MI350 series work, more large language models working on RDNA4 GPUs, and other enhancements.
